machining learning testing ground

To convert HGC gemc output into a text file, run it on jlab ifarm like

root -l -b -q 'analysis_hgc.C+("/volatile/halla/solid/sim/solid_gemc/cc_pro_JLAB_VERSION_1.3/withoutEC/cc_pro_SIDIS_He3_dirty_weighted_eDIS_CO2_filenum100_1e7.root","trigger",false,"single")'

The result is an output of text file called *_pixel.ml" with 3 columns separated by tab as 
"event number","pixel id","number of photon electron"
where pixel_id=16*64*sector+32*(31-pmt_y)+pmt_x

